<!--PageText-->
<div id='wikitext'>
<p>The code in <code>action_button.cxx</code> is correctly pulling in <code>armageddon_anim.png</code>, but it's not animating it.  The <strong>set_frame()</strong> command has no effect, it's just staying on the first frame.  Must be not turning on the animation when it loads the sprite.
</p><p class='vspace'></p>
<p>Or, the animation just flat out doesn't work correctly in that .png file.  I'm having issues with the builder.png and bomber.png displaying correctly as well. - <a class='wikilink' href='BomerAndBridgerAnimationDisapears'>Bomer and bridger animation disapears</a>
</p><p class='vspace'></p>
<p><a class='createlinktext' href='../Profiles/TomáBláha@action=edit'>Tomáš Bláha</a><a 
    class='createlink' href='../Profiles/TomáBláha@action=edit'>?</a> October 03, 2005, at 03:36 PM: I solved the problem with the armageddon button. (Also removing ending of comment without opening counterpart.): 
</p><p class='vspace'></p><pre>
diff -Nur trunk/data/data/core.xml trunk.new/data/data/core.xml
--- trunk/data/data/core.xml    2005-09-27 11:17:54.000000000 +0200
+++ trunk.new/data/data/core.xml        2005-10-03 21:10:00.000000000 +0200
@@ -123,8 +123,9 @@
       &lt;/sprite&gt;

       &lt;sprite name="armageddon_anim"&gt;
-        &lt;image file="../images/core/buttons/armageddon_anim.png"/&gt;
-        &lt;grid array="14,1" size="36,57" pos="0,0"/&gt;
+        &lt;image file="../images/core/buttons/armageddon_anim.png"&gt;
+          &lt;grid array="14,1" size="36,57" pos="0,0"/&gt;
+       &lt;/image&gt;
       &lt;/sprite&gt;
     &lt;/section&gt;
     &lt;section name="menu"&gt;
diff -Nur trunk/data/data/liquids.xml trunk.new/data/data/liquids.xml
--- trunk/data/data/liquids.xml 2005-01-29 10:29:10.000000000 +0100
+++ trunk.new/data/data/liquids.xml     2005-10-03 21:13:27.000000000 +0200
@@ -13,7 +13,7 @@
       &lt;animation speed="130" /&gt;
       &lt;image file="../images/liquids/water2.png"&gt;
         &lt;grid pos="0,0" size="64,64" array="8,1"/&gt;
-      &lt;/image&gt;--&gt;
+      &lt;/image&gt;
     &lt;/sprite&gt;
     &lt;sprite name="water3"&gt;
       &lt;image file="../images/liquids/water3.png"&gt;
